1. To install json server (npm insatll --save json-server)

2. To run json server (npx json-server --watch db.json)

3. To install lazy loading modules directly (ng g m <moduleName> --route <routingName> --module app.module)

4. npx kill-port 4200 (kill ng port)

5. npx kill-port 3000 (kill json server port)

6. To install fa-fa icons ( npm i angular-font-awesome )
    "node_modules/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css"

steps:
1. to install git hub pages (ng add angular-cli-ghpages) in project folder only.

2.in githubb click settting -> pages -> deploy from branch -> choose branch -> save

3.ng build --base-href "https://raja-raavi.github.io/ecommerceWebiste/"


